The paper discusses the use of POMDPs for autonomous systems, which is a topic that falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the use of formal methods for synthesizing supervisors, which falls under the categories of robotics (cs.RO) and systems and control (cs.SY). Finally, the paper proposes a learning-based algorithm for synthesizing supervisors, which falls under the category of software engineering (cs.SE).
